row.InputSentence1: Gina decided to bake an apple pie for the first time.
row.InputSentence2: She was extremely careful to follow the recipe exactly.
row.InputSentence3: After putting the pie in the oven, she eagerly waited to try it.
row.InputSentence4: It turned out to be delicious!
row.RandomFifthSentenceQuiz1: So she decided to throw it in the garbage.
row.RandomFifthSentenceQuiz2: She shared the recipe and the pie with all her friends.
